Package: semcache
Title: Local Semantic Cache for LLM Calls
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alejandro", "Jimenez Rico", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "aljrico@gmail.com")
Description: Local-first, persistent cache for large language model calls
    that supports exact caching via deterministic hashing and optional semantic
    caching via embedding similarity. Every cache entry is stored on disk in a
    readable, inspectable format, creating an automatic audit log. Semantic
    reuse is opt-in and conservative by default.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: digest
